overview.longBusinessSummary: NerdWallet, Inc. operates a digital platform that provides financial guidance to consumers and small and mid-sized businesses (SMB) in the United States, the United Kingdom, Australia, and Canada. The company's NerdWallet app delivers various financial products, such as credit cards, mortgages, insurance, SMB products, personal loans, banking, investing, and student loans. It also provides guidance to consumers through educational content, tools and calculators, and product marketplaces. NerdWallet, Inc. was founded in 2009 and is based in San Francisco, California.
